---
// No-op marker component. The rehype-section-wrapper plugin removes this
// from the tree before render and uses its position to start a new
// .prose-section (without requiring an h2). Subsequent content sits
// inside the new section until the next h2, <SectionBreak />, or
// <SectionResume />.
//
// Usage in MDX:
//
//   ## A section
//
//   Content inside the section card.
//
//   <SectionBreak />
//
//   Content here renders outside any section card.
//
//   <SectionResume />
//
//   Back inside a section card (without needing another h2).
//
// SectionBreak and SectionResume are globally available in MDX — no
// import needed.
---
